item.title: Men’s Lacrosse narrowly miss out on first silverware
item.author: David Thompson,
item.description: Following a hard fought victory over Swansea in the semis, Imperial Men’s Lacrosse faced up against Leeds Met Carnegie in the BUCS Trophy final in Sheffield on the 17th March. Leeds had narrowly beaten Birmingham in their semi and, having lost against Birmingham 20-0 two years previously, Imperial …
